  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Around the time that people discovered magic, there was a tribe
      of ancient sun worshipers called the Sun Dancers.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 10
    showTime: 10
    description: Two twins, Jaiden and Jairen SunDancer discovered that their traditional
      dances had the power to channel the sun.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 20
    showTime: 10
    description: Unlike magic, which leached the life force of the user, the sun
      did not corrupt anything when channeled.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 30
    showTime: 10
    description: The twins practiced their dancing until their ability to control
      the sun made them more powerful than even the strongest mages.
    nextOption: 
